"etiquette_manners_text1" = "The most important duty for a person performing Hajj and â€˜Umrah is sincerity before Allah. One must rid themselves of ostentation and the desire for fame in order to receive the reward for this Hajj and â€˜Umrah.

It is reported from Abu Hurayrah, may Allah be pleased with him, that the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said: 'Allah, the Most High, said: Â«I am entirely independent of needing any partner. Whoever performs any deed for My sake but also for someone else, I will leave him and his act of associating partners with Me!Â»' Muslim, 2985.

