"etiquette_manners_text6" = "A person performing Hajj and â€˜Umrah should engage in the remembrance of Allah (dhikr), supplications to Him (duâ€˜a), and seeking His forgiveness (istighfar). They should guard their tongue from anything except good speech. They should dedicate all their time to what will bring them benefit in this world and in the Hereafter.

