It is also reported from Ibn â€˜Abbas, may Allah be pleased with him and his father, that the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said: Â«Two blessings that many people fail to make use of: good health and free time.Â» Al-Bukhari 6412.";
"etiquette_manners_text7" = "A person performing Hajj and â€˜Umrah must avoid harming others through their words or actions.

