"hajj_step4_jamarat_title" = "Throwing Pebbles at the Three Pillars";
"hajj_step4_jamarat_text" = "The time for performing this rite begins after noon and lasts until nightfall. Each day, collect twenty-one pebbles slightly larger than a pea for throwing at the three pillars (seven for each pillar).

