Throw the pebbles at the Small Pillar one by one. With each throw of a pebble, pronounce the words â€œAllahu akbarâ€ (â€œAllah is the Greatestâ€). After completing the throwing at the first pillar, turn to face the Qiblah, raise your hands, and offer any supplication you wish.

